		<div class="paint-top"></div>
		<div class="home-description__content">
			<figure class="home-description__chef">
				<img src="{{ root }}/media/pizza-guy.png">
				<figcaption>
					<span class="text-smaller">Featured chef:</span>
					<br>
					<span class="text-bigger text-bold">Marcus Stern</span>
				</figcaption>
			</figure>

			<p>The Art of Cooking offers short classes throughout the year in our well equipped facilities that rival the best five star kitchens of the world. Learn from the chefs who concoct the most savory fare at Bellinghamâ€™s local restaurants and eateries.</p>
